{"service_name": "Forensic Readiness Assessment and Planning Services", "service_id": "5899340937691136", "company_name": "Amethyst Risk Management Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Amethyst Risk Management Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Forensic Readiness Assessment and Planning Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Amethyst can provide experienced support for the development of a cloud based Forensic Readiness capability that is matched to the needs of your business.  We can develop a Forensic Readiness Policy and the processes to ensure the continuity of digital evidence that it can be relied upon in legal proceedings.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Aligned to the HMG Forensic Readiness Principles\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides compliance with the Lawful Business Practise Regulations 2000\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Forensic Readiness capability integrated with other business processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business specific scenario based planning\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Development of KPI\u2019s and compliance reporting\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Digital evidence collected to a standard required by law\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Scenario based planning can lead to improved business processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Effective investigative capability is a potential deterrent to attackers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     With pre-planning major disruption to business can be avoided\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved understanding of business information, its use and locations\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3776 to \u00a31138 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92200/5899340937691136-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92200/5899340937691136-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92200/5899340937691136-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92200/5899340937691136-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n      